till tomorrow, unless you wanna carry it across.

22:36.787 --> 22:39.456
Alan!
Maybe we lucked out, and he's lost.

22:39.523 --> 22:42.559
Why don't you
give him a break? Up yours.

22:44.228 --> 22:46.630
Hey, Alan!

22:46.697 --> 22:49.466
What's goin' on
back there?

22:53.804 --> 22:57.874
<i>Alan!</i>
<i>Just the unique challenge</i> <i>of the great outdoors!</i>

22:59.810 --> 23:01.845
Shit.

