25:36.667 --> 25:39.569
You idiot!

25:43.340 --> 25:46.910
[ Mitch ]
All right! Whoo! Yeah!

25:46.977 --> 25:49.646
Whoo-hoo! Whoo-hoo!
All right! Oh, yeah!

25:49.713 --> 25:53.249
- <i>[ Chris ]</i>
<i>All right.</i> <i>- [ Mitch Whoops ]</i>

25:53.317 --> 25:57.421
- Alan, are you okay?
