- <i>What? Are you scared or</i>
<i>something? Move your ass!</i> <i>- Come on, Alan!</i>

26:00.424 --> 26:02.826
If I can do it, you can!
Can you do this?

26:02.893 --> 26:07.697
Yeah, I'm all right. I can
do it. I just got a pebble or something stuck in my shoe.

26:07.765 --> 26:11.268
-It's no big deal. We can wait.
-No, no. You guys go ahead. I'll find you.

26:11.335 --> 26:14.738
[ George ] I bet you
he's too scared to cross. [ Mitch ] Leave him alone.

26:14.805 --> 26:18.275
All right, Alan! You come when
you're ready. The trail's real plain. You can find it.

26:18.342 --> 26:21.745
<i>[ Alan ] Okay.</i>
<i>I'll come back for you in</i> <i>a while if you're not there.</i>

26:21.812 --> 26:25.782
