I can't even believe this!
Do you believe this? I can believe it.

29:21.058 --> 29:23.527
I don't believe it.
I'm sleepin' in your tent, asshole.

29:23.594 --> 29:26.263
Come on! You know
we needed those poles. Where'd you put 'em?

29:26.330 --> 29:28.532
