come back in here?

35:53.116 --> 35:56.185
Shut up! Shut up,
guys! Shut up!

35:56.253 --> 36:00.523
Shut up.
Yeah, right. [ Screams, Laughs ]

36:02.359 --> 36:06.563
[ George ]
