36:06.630 --> 36:10.100
<i>[ Mitch ] Where did it go?</i>
<i>Where did it go?</i> <i>All right.</i>

36:10.167 --> 36:13.370
[ All Talking At Once ]

36:13.436 --> 36:18.107
How we do, guys?
