36:20.377 --> 36:23.513
<i>[ George ]</i>
<i>Frogs.</i> <i>I struck out, man.</i>

36:23.580 --> 36:26.816
[ Laughs ] Holy shit!
Look at dickface! Whoa!

36:26.883 --> 36:29.552
All right, man!
Way to go!

36:29.619 --> 36:32.021
<i>[ George ] Good job.</i>
<i>Some haul, Alan.</i> <i>Yeah, well,</i>

36:32.088 --> 36:33.756
I really feel one
with nature today.

36:33.823 --> 36:36.258
Must be six or seven
in there. I can't believe that.

36:36.326 --> 36:40.663
- <i>[ Chris ] How'd you do it?</i>
<i>- No big deal.</i> <i>-</i> <i>[ Metal Clanking ]</i>

36:43.200 --> 36:46.469
