36:51.875 --> 36:56.012
"Neat"? No.
I don't think that's neat. What do you guys think?

36:58.615 --> 37:01.451
Hey, wait a second.
Hey, I caught those. No, you didn't.

37:01.518 --> 37:04.153
Not the right way,
you didn't. Oh, you mean <i>your</i> way.

37:04.221 --> 37:08.325
No! I mean
the <i>right</i> way.

37:08.391 --> 37:12.728
You know, you're a smart kid,
Alan, but you really let me down this time.

37:12.796 --> 37:15.265
You let yourself down.

