So what do you say you
clean the fish Chris and I caught before we leave?

37:20.103 --> 37:21.971
Then we can forget
about your little trick. No!

37:22.038 --> 37:25.174
Well, I could help him.
No. No. This is Alan's job.

37:25.242 --> 37:29.479
Come here. Come here.
I'll show ya. Nothin' to it.

37:34.284 --> 37:35.985
Ohh.

37:36.052 --> 37:39.121
All right?
