37:39.189 --> 37:42.825
Nothin' to it.
[ Grunting ]

37:46.930 --> 37:48.831
[ Continues Grunting ]

37:51.835 --> 37:54.504
[ Panting ]

37:57.073 --> 38:00.743
Now why don't you
clean the rest of these, and we'll finish loadin' the canoe.

38:00.810 --> 38:03.946
No. No way.

38:04.014 --> 38:08.284
You'll do it,
