- I got you anchored. You're not gonna fall.

59:59.528 --> 01:00:03.565
- Oh, Jesus, Vic.
I can't do this. - You can... if you try.

01:00:03.632 --> 01:00:06.267
For Christ's sake, Vic,
I can't do it!

01:00:06.335 --> 01:00:09.771
- Don't you understand?
I can't do it! - Then that's where you'll stay.

01:00:09.838 --> 01:00:13.074
- What?
- Vic! - What do you mean?

01:00:13.141 --> 01:00:16.711
What are you doing?
You can't just leave him there. You can't just let him hang.

01:00:16.778 --> 01:00:19.747
- Alan, we'll meet you
down below. - Vic, where are you going?

01:00:19.815 --> 01:00:21.950
He said he couldn't do it!
[ All Shouting ]

01:00:22.017 --> 01:00:24.786
Vic, the guy is
scared to death! You can't leave him hanging!

01:00:24.853 --> 01:00:28.356
- <i>Vic, come back!</i>
<i>You can't just leave me here!</i> <i>- You can't! You're crazy!</i>

01:00:28.423 --> 01:00:30.091
<i>What if he falls?</i>
<i>He could die out there!</i>

01:00:30.158 --> 01:00:33.394
Vic, please!
Mitch. George.

01:00:33.462 --> 01:00:36.364
<i>Mitch. Vic!</i>
<i>Come on.</i>

01:00:36.431 --> 01:00:38.566
Where you goin'? Vic!

01:00:38.634 --> 01:00:42.404
<i>I'm telling the truth, Vic.</i>
<i>I'm scared. Mitch.</i> <i>Move it!</i>

01:00:42.471 --> 01:00:44.406
Don't leave without me.
Please. No!

01:00:44.473 --> 01:00:46.408
<i>Don't leave, Mitch!</i>

01:00:49.578 --> 01:00:51.646
<i>[ Vic ]</i>
<i>Let's go!</i>

01:01:01.556 --> 01:01:04.592
Vic, you're not just gonna
leave him there, are you? Yeah, I am.

01:01:04.660 --> 01:01:07.295
For how long?
It's up to Alan.

01:01:07.362 --> 01:01:09.530
But, Vic, h-he's scared.
He can't just--

01:01:09.598 --> 01:01:12.133
He can... if he tries.

01:01:12.200 --> 01:01:15.870
What if he doesn't try, huh?
Come on, Vic. Can't you just get him down this once?

01:01:15.937 --> 01:01:19.607
Well, someday I'm not gonna
be there to get him down. Then what's he gonna do?

01:01:19.675 --> 01:01:25.380
Why are you doin' this?
I am not doin' anything. Alan is doin' this to himself.

01:01:25.447 --> 01:01:28.383
Now, is that a problem
for you, Chris?

01:01:30.719 --> 01:01:33.288
Yeah, it <i>is</i> a problem.

01:01:33.355 --> 01:01:35.290
I'm goin' back.

01:01:42.731 --> 01:01:46.034
This is not
acceptable behavior.

01:01:46.101 --> 01:01:47.869
[ Gasping ]
Is that clear?

01:02:21.369 --> 01:02:26.240
[ Clears Throat ]
We'll camp here for the night. Okay with you guys?

01:02:46.528 --> 01:02:49.931
[ Grunting ]

01:03:05.380 --> 01:03:07.315
[ Panting ]

01:04:27.262 --> 01:04:29.631
[ Panting ]

01:04:37.239 --> 01:04:40.408
All right. Do it.

01:04:46.848 --> 01:04:49.050
[ Grunting ]

01:05:03.431 --> 01:05:05.666
[ Panting ]

01:05:19.614 --> 01:05:23.884
The way I figure it,
we won't go back to the old campsite downstream.

01:05:23.952 --> 01:05:26.754
No, we'll go north.
We'll follow the great bear.

01:05:26.821 --> 01:05:30.391
You were wrong--
what you did to Alan, Vic. He's right, man.

01:05:30.458 --> 01:05:34.228
<i>You must be crazy,</i>
<i>leaving him up there.</i> <i>No.</i>

01:05:34.296 --> 01:05:36.364
Yeah. Yeah, we'll go north.

01:05:36.431 --> 01:05:38.499
- Vic, I don't know why
you're doing this, but-- - What's that?

01:05:38.566 --> 01:05:40.067
Shh!

01:05:46.141 --> 01:05:49.744
It's Alan! You did it!
Son of a bitch.

01:05:49.811 --> 01:05:51.679
<i>You did it, man!</i>
<i>Way to go, Alan!</i> <i>You did it!</i>

01:05:51.746 --> 01:05:54.882
You made it! All right!
<i>Way to go, man!</i>

01:05:54.950 --> 01:05:58.920
All right! Way to go!
Are you all right? I don't believe it!

01:05:58.987 --> 01:06:01.656
[ Laughing ]
I knew you could-- I'm goin' home.

01:06:01.723 --> 01:06:06.060
Wait. Well, you can't.
You don't understand. Don't you see? You did great!

01:06:06.127 --> 01:06:08.195
I knew you would.
Don't you see that?

01:06:08.263 --> 01:06:10.898
We're all together again.
Come on, we did it! Yeah, I did it.

01:06:10.966 --> 01:06:13.768
Fuck you. I could have died.
He's right, man.

01:06:15.103 --> 01:06:18.005
Alan--
Alan, you don't understand.

01:06:18.073 --> 01:06:20.375
None of that matters now.
Look at you!

01:06:20.442 --> 01:06:24.679
Look at what you did.
You made it! I-I did that for you.

01:06:24.746 --> 01:06:27.815
I'm goin' home.
Me too, Vic. You gotta take us home.

01:06:27.882 --> 01:06:31.252
We wanna go home!
What's the matter with you? You don't want to miss tomorrow.

01:06:31.319 --> 01:06:35.122
Come on! We're goin' north!
I can show you wolves up there. I can show you mountain lion--

01:06:35.190 --> 01:06:37.759
Bye, Vic.

01:06:37.826 --> 01:06:40.461
Alan, wait.
Wait! Wait.

01:06:40.528 --> 01:06:42.963
Where you gonna go?
It's gonna get dark.

01:06:43.031 --> 01:06:45.099
You need me, guys. You'll never
get down the mountain by yourselves.

01:06:45.166 --> 01:06:46.967
I don't care.
I'm goin' home. No, you're not!

01:06:47.035 --> 01:06:50.405
I'm responsible for you guys.
We're goin' home, Vic!

01:06:55.677 --> 01:06:58.780
[ Chuckles ]
Chris--

01:06:58.847 --> 01:07:01.149
You can't. You can't.
You understand? You can't leave.

01:07:02.617 --> 01:07:04.885
You can't leave.

01:07:04.953 --> 01:07:07.188
Chris. Chris,
what are you doin'? Go. Get outta here.

01:07:07.255 --> 01:07:09.257
Go!
Don't leave.

01:07:09.324 --> 01:07:11.926
You can't leave.
We're a team. Do you hear me?

01:07:15.330 --> 01:07:17.398
You can't leave me.

01:07:45.794 --> 01:07:49.197
We've been walkin' for hours.
It's 'cause we've been walking in circles.

01:07:51.599 --> 01:07:54.668
<i>[ Bird Calls Eerily ]</i>

01:07:58.139 --> 01:08:00.941
It's too dark.
We gotta camp.

01:08:01.009 --> 01:08:03.511
I think I like that plan.
Yeah.

01:08:23.997 --> 01:08:26.233
Think we'll ever
get outta here?

01:08:28.870 --> 01:08:33.374
Chris?
I can't believe Vic did this.

01:08:33.441 --> 01:08:36.844
How could he?
How could he do this?

01:08:39.948 --> 01:08:43.952
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>♪ In the quiet</i> <i>of the evening ♪</i>

01:08:47.388 --> 01:08:51.058
<i>♪ Where the deep</i>
<i>blue waters run ♪</i>

01:08:54.662 --> 01:08:59.265
<i>♪ Paradise is casting shadows ♪</i>

01:09:02.036 --> 01:09:06.040
<i>♪ On the heart</i>
<i>of her own son ♪</i>

01:09:09.377 --> 01:09:13.581
<i>♪ Since the fatherland</i>
<i>of Eden ♪</i>

01:09:16.885 --> 01:09:20.287
<i>♪ Where we roamed</i>
<i>cathedral woods ♪</i>

01:09:24.192 --> 01:09:28.796
<i>♪ We have fought</i>
<i>the lonely silence ♪</i>

01:09:31.698 --> 01:09:35.202
<i>♪ Learned to live</i>
<i>misunderstood ♪</i>

01:09:37.205 --> 01:09:40.774
Look. Yeah.
<i>♪ Oh-oh, oh-oh ♪</i>

01:09:40.841 --> 01:09:42.777
<i>♪ Paradise ♪</i>

01:09:42.844 --> 01:09:45.212
<i>I told ya I'd find it.</i>

01:09:45.279 --> 01:09:49.984
<i>♪ Oh, all alone</i>
<i>in paradise ♪</i> <i>[ Laughing ]</i>

01:09:51.719 --> 01:09:55.089
We did it. The canoe--
We actually found the canoe!

01:09:55.156 --> 01:09:57.224
You did it, Alan!
All right!

01:09:57.292 --> 01:10:01.229
We made it! All right!
Yeah! Awesome!

01:10:01.296 --> 01:10:05.767
Let's get this mother home!
All right, we're homeward bound. Yeah!

01:10:07.802 --> 01:10:11.005
<i>Yeah.</i>
<i>Yeah! All right!</i>

01:10:11.072 --> 01:10:13.707
<i>Yeah!</i>
<i>All right, that's it!</i>

01:10:13.775 --> 01:10:17.812
This thing is over now!
Nobody is going anywhere.

01:10:17.879 --> 01:10:20.348
<i>Vic, please,</i>
<i>leave us alone!</i> <i>No!</i>

01:10:20.415 --> 01:10:24.519
Look, you are not leaving.
Damn it, Vic, we're goin' home, all right?

01:10:24.586 --> 01:10:29.324
No, you're not!
You are not going home. I am not gonna let you.

01:10:29.390 --> 01:10:31.625
[ Grunts ]
Leave him alone!

01:10:31.693 --> 01:10:36.364
<i>Vic!</i>
<i>Stop, Vic!</i>

01:10:37.865 --> 01:10:40.901
- <i>Stop!</i>
<i>- I'm gonna kill you, Vic!</i>

01:10:40.969 --> 01:10:43.805
- Chris! What are you doing?
- Stay away from us!

01:10:43.871 --> 01:10:47.908
- I'm gonna kill you!
- Chris, stop! Stop it, Chris!

01:10:50.044 --> 01:10:52.379
No! Let go!
Give me that!

01:10:54.716 --> 01:10:57.351
- Son of a bitch!
- [ Groans ]

01:10:58.886 --> 01:11:00.387
Jesus!
Oh, my God!

01:11:14.068 --> 01:11:17.805
[ Bone Crunches ]
[ Screams ]

01:11:21.209 --> 01:11:24.245
[ Panting, Whimpering ]

01:11:47.969 --> 01:11:50.104
All right, good.
More slack.

01:11:51.172 --> 01:11:53.774
All right, good.
Hold it.

01:11:53.841 --> 01:11:55.142
That's good.

01:11:57.345 --> 01:11:59.680
<i>Put some</i>
<i>in that pocket there.</i> <i>There you go, guys.</i>

01:11:59.747 --> 01:12:02.182
I'm tellin' ya,
this is never gonna work. Yes, it will.

01:12:02.250 --> 01:12:04.318
Shut up and get
the other pack.

01:12:06.054 --> 01:12:09.791
Okay, you got it?
Okay. Get it around you!

01:12:14.095 --> 01:12:17.298
Put the rope
underneath your arms.

01:12:22.704 --> 01:12:26.040
Come on, come on.
Hurry up, you guys.

01:12:26.107 --> 01:12:28.476
All right.
Good and tight.

01:12:32.313 --> 01:12:34.481
<i>[ Alan ]</i>
<i>Hurry up, Vic!</i>

01:12:36.384 --> 01:12:38.919
Okay. Good.
Now, hold on, Vic. Let's go.

01:12:38.986 --> 01:12:41.488
All right.
[ Grunting ]

01:12:48.730 --> 01:12:50.498
You okay?

01:13:00.007 --> 01:13:02.509
[ Grunting ]
Help me, George.

01:13:14.322 --> 01:13:16.991
<i>[ Alan ]</i>
<i>Easy, easy!</i>

01:13:23.765 --> 01:13:26.000
[ Grunting ]
He's almost here.

01:13:26.067 --> 01:13:28.869
Hold on, man.
You're all right.

01:13:32.507 --> 01:13:34.609
[ Panting ]

01:13:34.675 --> 01:13:36.977
[ Grunting ]

01:13:37.044 --> 01:13:40.047
He's almost here.
Here, hold me. Hold me.

01:13:40.114 --> 01:13:42.049
Okay. That's all right.

01:13:44.085 --> 01:13:48.456
Gimme your hand.
Gimme your hand! Okay.

01:13:53.561 --> 01:13:55.663
I got him. Got him!

01:13:55.730 --> 01:13:58.265
[ Panting ]

01:14:00.234 --> 01:14:03.470
Easy. Right here.
Here.

01:14:06.274 --> 01:14:08.576
I'll get
the first-aid stuff. Hurry.

01:14:10.144 --> 01:14:12.479
Oh, jeez,
he looks awful. Yeah.

01:14:12.547 --> 01:14:14.815
I'd better stay with him while
you guys go downriver for help.

01:14:14.882 --> 01:14:17.184
No, we'll just leave him here
and send help back for him.

01:14:17.251 --> 01:14:20.354
- Somebody's gotta
stay with him. - Alan, he left you!

01:14:20.421 --> 01:14:22.489
I don't care. It's not the same
thing. He's hurt.

01:14:22.557 --> 01:14:25.359
- How the hell are we gonna
find the ranger station? - You'll find it.

01:14:25.426 --> 01:14:27.528
You figure the river'll
lead us down?

01:14:27.595 --> 01:14:31.298
Yeah. Just remember to keep
the sun at your left.

01:14:31.365 --> 01:14:35.969
All right.
We'll get someone here as soon as we can.

01:14:36.037 --> 01:14:38.606
Put that over him.

01:14:44.078 --> 01:14:48.048
<i>All you have to do is</i>
<i>hike downstream. You'll reach</i> <i>the ranger station by tomorrow.</i>

01:14:48.115 --> 01:14:50.450
Sure you'll be all right?

01:14:50.518 --> 01:14:53.487
Yeah, I'm sure.
We're outta here.

01:14:54.555 --> 01:14:56.490
Good luck, Alan, huh?

01:15:03.531 --> 01:15:06.967
See ya soon,
all right? Yeah. Bye.

01:15:19.080 --> 01:15:21.582
[ Clears Throat ]

01:15:42.003 --> 01:15:44.071
The others went for help.

01:15:50.811 --> 01:15:54.614
<i>You know,</i>
<i>that thing you rigged--</i> <i>it saved my life.</i>

01:15:56.217 --> 01:15:59.553
Thanks.
Thanks a lot.

01:16:04.425 --> 01:16:07.694
Makin' fire.
Yeah.

01:16:09.196 --> 01:16:11.231
How come you're
doin' it that way?

01:16:11.299 --> 01:16:16.203
<i>I thought you hated</i>
<i>all that stuff.</i> <i>We sort of lost the matches.</i>

01:16:34.255 --> 01:16:36.223
<i>[ Pained Breathing ]</i>

01:16:37.725 --> 01:16:41.729
[ Laughs ]
This wasn't on the itinerary.

01:16:41.796 --> 01:16:44.198
At first light,
we're takin' the river.

01:16:47.168 --> 01:16:49.236
I thought you said
help was comin'.

01:16:51.005 --> 01:16:52.740
Change of plans.

01:16:54.609 --> 01:16:59.080
Alan, you can't
take the canoe.

01:16:59.146 --> 01:17:03.550
It's too dangerous.
Y-You don't know how to--

01:17:03.618 --> 01:17:07.288
We'll just
wait here for help. We can't.

01:17:07.355 --> 01:17:11.392
Your leg is broken.
You're losin' a ton of blood.

01:17:21.268 --> 01:17:23.069
[ Sighs ]

01:17:41.656 --> 01:17:43.791
I'll do whatever I can
to help.

01:20:34.829 --> 01:20:37.331
[ Gasps ]

01:21:14.735 --> 01:21:17.003
Vic!

01:21:17.805 --> 01:21:19.239
<i>Vic!</i>

01:21:32.019 --> 01:21:34.021
Vic!

01:21:34.889 --> 01:21:36.991
[ Coughing ]

01:21:51.805 --> 01:21:55.341
Don't worry, Vic.
You're comin' around!

01:21:59.246 --> 01:22:03.750
<i>You're comin'!</i>
<i>Reach out! I got you!</i> <i>Put out your arm! Grab!</i>

01:22:04.985 --> 01:22:08.655
Reach! Grab my hand!

01:22:13.794 --> 01:22:17.197
Hold on. You got it.
You got it.

01:22:17.264 --> 01:22:19.766
[ Grunting ]
Pull. Pull.

01:22:30.577 --> 01:22:33.880
Hell of a ride, huh?

01:22:33.948 --> 01:22:37.051
Remind me to put it
on the tour next year.

01:22:37.952 --> 01:22:39.687
How's your leg?

01:22:40.921 --> 01:22:43.657
It's been numb
most of the way.

01:22:51.498 --> 01:22:52.966
Oh, man.

01:22:55.135 --> 01:22:57.837
What you did back there--
that was brave.

01:22:57.905 --> 01:23:01.975
It took guts.
I didn't do this 'cause I wanted to.

01:23:02.042 --> 01:23:04.978
It wasn't fun,
and I wouldn't do it again.

01:23:05.045 --> 01:23:07.080
I mean, what's the point?
We didn't make it anyway.

01:23:07.147 --> 01:23:10.617
The point is,
you made it down that river.

01:23:10.684 --> 01:23:15.121
I was trying to get you
to a doctor. I don't give a shit about the river.

01:23:17.291 --> 01:23:21.962
You...
are the most stubborn... son of a bitch!

01:23:22.796 --> 01:23:25.064
Except maybe for you.

01:23:34.775 --> 01:23:38.445
How did your father
ever talk you into comin' this summer?

01:23:40.447 --> 01:23:45.118
I was young.
It won't happen again.

01:24:00.100 --> 01:24:03.736
<i>Alan, it's our ride home!</i>
<i>We made it! Whoo!</i>

01:24:03.804 --> 01:24:06.173
Yeah! Yeah!
Whoo!

01:24:06.240 --> 01:24:09.309
Hey, we're here!
Hey! Whoo!

01:24:09.376 --> 01:24:11.678
<i>♪ Runnin' outta self-control ♪</i>

01:24:11.745 --> 01:24:15.115
<i>♪ Gettin' close</i>
<i>to an overload ♪</i>

01:24:15.182 --> 01:24:18.785
<i>♪ Up against</i>
<i>a no-win situation ♪</i> <i>Whoa, whoa. Wait a minute.</i>

01:24:18.852 --> 01:24:21.421
<i>♪ [ Stops ]</i>
<i>You hear music, you see</i> <i>credits, you think it's over?</i>

01:24:21.488 --> 01:24:25.058
I gotta tell you what happened
to Chris, Mitch and George.

01:24:25.125 --> 01:24:28.495
They made it
to the ranger station, grumbling somethin' about bad directions.

01:24:28.562 --> 01:24:32.599
What did I know?
I was in charge. I had to say <i>something.</i>

01:24:32.666 --> 01:24:35.335
[ Sighs ]
I made my peace with Vic,

01:24:35.402 --> 01:24:37.303
and I learned somethin' too:

01:24:37.371 --> 01:24:40.307
Everybody needs
a time of isolation,

01:24:40.374 --> 01:24:42.409
time to be one with nature.

01:24:42.476 --> 01:24:47.280
So, every year I come
to these woods to contemplate my place in the universe,

01:24:47.347 --> 01:24:49.182
fish, to live off the land.

01:24:49.249 --> 01:24:52.285
<i>[ Alan Narrates ]</i>
<i>I know what you're thinking:</i>

01:24:52.352 --> 01:24:54.253
<i>I've lost my mind.</i>

01:24:54.321 --> 01:24:58.358
<i>After all this--</i>
<i>the bridge, the cliff,</i>

01:24:58.425 --> 01:25:02.262
<i>the group pee,</i>
<i>the boat over the waterfall--</i>

01:25:02.329 --> 01:25:05.765
<i>and</i> now
<i>I come back to the woods?</i>

01:25:05.833 --> 01:25:08.101
<i>Not</i> this <i>puppy.</i>

01:25:08.168 --> 01:25:11.271
<i>♪ Runnin' outta self-control ♪</i>

01:25:11.338 --> 01:25:14.274
<i>♪ Gettin' close</i>
<i>to an overload ♪</i>

01:25:14.341 --> 01:25:18.244
<i>♪ Up against</i>
<i>a no-win situation ♪</i>

01:25:20.481 --> 01:25:23.717
<i>♪ Shoulder to shoulder</i>
<i>push and shove ♪</i>

01:25:23.784 --> 01:25:27.087
<i>♪ I'm hangin' up</i>
<i>my boxing gloves ♪</i>

01:25:27.154 --> 01:25:32.292
<i>♪ I'm heading for</i>
<i>a long vacation ♪</i>

01:25:32.359 --> 01:25:34.294
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

01:25:34.361 --> 01:25:37.364
<i>♪ Be good to yourself ♪</i>
<i>♪ You be good to yourself ♪</i>

01:25:37.431 --> 01:25:41.635
<i>♪ When nobody else will ♪</i>
<i>♪ When nobody else will ♪</i>

01:25:41.702 --> 01:25:44.805
<i>♪ Oh, be good to yourself ♪</i>

01:25:47.441 --> 01:25:50.744
<i>♪ You're walkin' a high wire ♪</i>
<i>♪ You're walkin' a high wire ♪</i>

01:25:50.811 --> 01:25:54.581
<i>♪ Caught in a cross fire ♪</i>
<i>♪ Caught in a cross fire ♪</i>

01:25:54.648 --> 01:25:58.618
<i>♪ Oh, be good to yourself ♪</i>

01:26:00.020 --> 01:26:02.489
<i>♪ When you can't give no more ♪</i>

01:26:02.556 --> 01:26:05.592
<i>♪ They want it all</i>
<i>but you gotta say no ♪</i>

